---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const title = 'Contact | wrongfuldeathcalc.com';
const description = 'How to reach the editorial team at wrongfuldeathcalc.com — corrections, content suggestions, press inquiries.';
---
<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <h1>Contact</h1>

  <p>wrongfuldeathcalc.com is a small editorial site run by The Click Lab. We read every message but do not provide legal advice and do not respond to case-specific intake. If you have an active wrongful death claim, please contact an attorney licensed in your state. We cannot help with intake, attorney referrals, or case-specific questions.</p>

  <h2>What we respond to</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Corrections.</strong> Factual errors, outdated state statutes, mischaracterized rules. Send the page URL, the specific claim you're correcting, and your source.</li>
    <li><strong>Content suggestions.</strong> Topics in the wrongful death space you wish we covered &mdash; a specific state's statute structure, a damage category we haven't addressed, a calculator improvement.</li>
    <li><strong>Advertising and partnerships.</strong> We monetize through Google AdSense only and do not accept direct sponsorships, attorney referral arrangements, or paid placements. Editorial guest content has to meet our independence standard; almost all commercial pitches don't.</li>
    <li><strong>Press inquiries.</strong> Happy to be cited in articles and educational materials.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>What we don't do</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Case intake. We are not attorneys.</li>
    <li>Attorney referrals. We don't have an attorney panel.</li>
    <li>Document review. Don't send settlement offers, medical records, police reports, or correspondence.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How to reach us</h2>
  <p>Email: <a href="mailto:hey@theclicklab.agency">hey@theclicklab.agency</a></p>
  <p>Subject line conventions:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><code>[CORRECTION] page-url</code></li>
    <li><code>[SUGGESTION] topic</code></li>
    <li><code>[PRESS]</code></li>
  </ul>
  <p>We respond to most messages within 3&ndash;5 business days. We do not respond to AI-generated form letters, mass outreach for backlinks, or attorney lead-gen pitches.</p>

  <h2>Operating address</h2>
  <p>The Click Lab<br />
  Editorial correspondence, wrongfuldeathcalc.com<br />
  hey@theclicklab.agency</p>
</BaseLayout>
